{"TopicId":192690,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"How is your space program responding to Covid 19","CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-03-27T19:29:36Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-03-27T19:29:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre your kerbals all ok? Did anyone get sick?\u003Cbr\u003E\nWhat precautions have you put in place? I for one, have been focusing on hygiene and Social distancing.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy kerbals\u00A0have been keeping away from each other, (and keeping their helmets on)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PgcrDtv.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/PgcrDtv.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame with my Satellites\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qu128bG.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/qu128bG.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Mega Munar Load Lifter has been busy keeping base modules apart:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00222QsWVf5.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2QsWVf5.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn space, we\u0027re having a one kerbal per pod strategy, and the pods have been spread out too:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022WLURHY0.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/WLURHY0.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, we\u0027ve been making sure we keep important surfaces like door handles clean, washing them down with liquid sanitizer:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00225ZoHPVd.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/5ZoHPVd.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe kerbals also.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022IDgdWwi.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002262.19\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/IDgdWwi.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat are you trying? Is there something else I could be doing?\u003Cbr\u003E\nStay safe.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-03-27T19:35:12Z\u0022 title=\u002203/27/2020 07:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 27, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Tw1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-03-29T06:15:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy Kerbal scientists have discovered that the fresh natural vacuum is the best countermeasure.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso don\u0027t forget to wash your helmet glasses with rocket fuel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"purpleivan","CreatedById":120081,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-03-29T07:20:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s presented some challenges to the engeering dept at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, but there was no arguing with the medics on this one, if operations were to continue offworld.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDefinitely better to play it safe, than be real sorry.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022D2fp8p3.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/D2fp8p3.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PNprIBz.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/PNprIBz.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stamp20","CreatedById":202020,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-03-30T15:33:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo effect, Kerbal doctors have not found any coronavirus cases in my save file. Although, reports from my Mun base say Bill has been coughing a lot, so...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dirkidirk","CreatedById":200064,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-03-30T16:27:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/XAXegAbfneo?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nso far I have not taken any measures to protect my kerbals against this, although I may soon build some orbital missiles to fire upon infected spacecraft and bases, only if it gets bad enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sepone","CreatedById":203414,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T12:29:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003EThis morning the nyan cat flew across my loading screen. At first I thought \u003Cstrong\u003Eit\u0027s a virus\u003C/strong\u003E!!!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003EBut luckily it was just an april fool. Phew... \u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022i6d9b8jp.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002251.68\u0022 height=\u0022370\u0022 width=\u0022716\u0022 src=\u0022https://s19.directupload.net/images/200401/i6d9b8jp.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003ETake care of your Kerbals and \u003Cstrong\u003Estay healthy\u003C/strong\u003E!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-02T16:55:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223762918\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192690\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585466404\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022120081\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022purpleivan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/29/2020 at 6:20 PM, purpleivan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s presented some challenges to the engeering dept at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, but there was no arguing with the medics on this one, if operations were to continue offworld.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow that is some proper social distancing right there.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223762907\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192690\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585462536\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/29/2020 at 5:15 PM, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy Kerbal scientists have discovered that the fresh natural vacuum is the best countermeasure.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso don\u0027t forget to wash your helmet glasses with rocket fuel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMonopropellant works pretty well, just got to avoid breathing. But you\u0027re supposed to be careful what you breathe in anyway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223763572\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192690\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585585621\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200064\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dirkidirk\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/31/2020 at 3:27 AM, Dirkidirk said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nso far I have not taken any measures to protect my kerbals against this, although I may soon build some orbital missiles to fire upon infected spacecraft and bases, only if it gets bad enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat looks pretty serious, you should probably do that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMeanwhile, in my copy of KSP, things are getting worse and worse.\u00A0 Across the solar system Kerbals are taking action.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022a3Jk2Ar.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/a3Jk2Ar.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Mun has gone into lockdown, with strict quarantine rules in place\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00225e4msTd.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/5e4msTd.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMinimus has closed for business.\u00A0 They want to be very clear about that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022QNEeVFv.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/QNEeVFv.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022xm5WhHU.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/xm5WhHU.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn kerbin, drastic measures have been put in place. No one is allowed out in groups more than two. Patrolling drones will find those who don\u0027t comply.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022lIaQwY3.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/lIaQwY3.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002267.33\u0022 width=\u00221157\u0022 alt=\u0022slIIs5X.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/slIIs5X.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThose that do go out must be accompanied by a retrofitted rover, to ensure the right distance is maintained.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022CqFE0S2.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/CqFE0S2.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo one is allowed in or out of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E. The military has been called upon to enforce this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00222ghYV5W.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2ghYV5W.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022TourrEa.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/TourrEa.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMobile Amphibious Eve Micro Bases have been repurposed as tanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022tAET0sM.png\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/tAET0sM.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s looking pretty intense right now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-02T17:12:57Z\u0022 title=\u002204/02/2020 05:12  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 2, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Tw1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dirkidirk","CreatedById":200064,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-02T17:21:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223765259\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192690\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585846530\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002259717\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tw1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Tw1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[snipped for brevity]\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/tAET0sM.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022tAET0sM.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/tAET0sM.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s looking pretty intense right now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think I see a face on the side of that tank\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-02T19:29:21Z\u0022 title=\u002204/02/2020 07:29  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 2, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Vanamonde\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Generic username","CreatedById":203807,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-06T18:53:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbold of you to assume kerbals can catch viruses\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Manwith Noname","CreatedById":117203,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-07T03:45:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe introduced a social distancing policy some time ago. At first, things seemed to be going well but apparently our employees just cannot help but be a bit touchy feely.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022EC78283AA965EED38E81AAC6F9A342B2BDD344DA\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/1013814925696259434/EC78283AA965EED38E81AAC6F9A342B2BDD344DA/\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ArtemisAZ","CreatedById":179669,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-07T10:13:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFrantically trying to find someway to reverse engineer it for use as a bio weapon in our war against the vile dolphin scourge.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Clockwork13","CreatedById":100102,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-16T00:25:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmost of my kerbals (the useful ones anyways) have already been launched into deep space, so they are safe from the kerona virus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}